    "name": "Auger Angling",
    "description": "When a nearby target's Arts Reaction or Originium Crystals are consumed, opens an angling hole beneath the enemy that deals Physical DMG and recovers SP. The skill has a chance to hook a Rare Fin that greatly increases the DMG dealt and recovers extra SP. T2 Veteran Angler improves the Rare Fin catching chance by +0.2%/+0.5% per 10 Intellect (cap +30%). P3 May the Willing Bite applies a 10s +15% ATK team buff on Rare Fin catches.",
